		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Free Lakrissa from MOO and have her return to Haven.&#xD;&#xA;loadlevel SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;oe debugbook &gt; act two setup &gt; tiefling path&#xD;&#xA;&gt; go to region &gt; act 2 &gt; haven &gt; after checkpoint&#xD;&#xA;oe prisonersreturn &gt; teleport S_DEN_Tiefling_010&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to Lakrissa or Alfira in Haven once they are together." />
